Jazz Jackrabbit 2 for CSS - Ghostly Antics - Deathrun map.
==========================================================

V. 1.0 Final
------------


Gameplay:
-----------
Do you know Jazz Jackrabbit 2, one of the best platformer of 1998?
Here you can get deathrun map inspired by one of it's level!

Inside:
----------
- 22 CT spawn
- 2 TT spawn
- 13 traps
- Weapon select at end of map
- Speed and music select at end of map
- 2 small secrets
- AFK Timer - one minute...
- ... then 20 seconds for every trap

________

Installation:
-------------
Decompress files:

- deathrun_JazzJackrabbit2_GA.bsp
- deathrun_JazzJackrabbit2_GA.txt

To your cstrike/maps folder.

Have fun!


Support Jazz Jackrabbit 2 community and learn more about JJ2!
Visit:

- http://www.jazz2online.com/
- http://www.jazzjackrabbit.net/

Map by: nkpkiller / 2012 , POLAND

All rights reserved to Epic Games for making Jazz Jackrabbit 2.


Download size: 9MB

This map is based on the movie Indiana Jones, specifically the one where Indiana Jones is chased by a boulder in a cave. It has in total 14 traps, so it's not too easy, but not too hard.

Two of the traps are automatic, the moving walls at the start and the spinning platforms about 3/4 of the way through, so have fun! At the end, you now get a hat with your shotgun, so you can feel and look like Indie himself!

Thanks for downloading!

~ Sneeza

This map is based in a factory-type setting.The map is not too long but it is a little difficult when you get to the end. There are about 11 or so traps, and a couple of new ideas. This map stays true to its name 'illusions' where, at the end of the map, there is an illusion maze that the opposing team will have to navigate though. Then comes the tricky part. The trappers will get to choose the course of the maze. Here, is a choice of three buttons which all create a separate path route for the other team to take a chance and cross.

deathrun_iceworld_v2 by 'cS.Metz * UPDATE: March 6th 2011 * Fixed Terrorist team bugs due to engine update. Sorry it took so long to fix, I haven't really been mapping recently. Please replace v2 with v2fix to fully enjoy my map once more. :) Information: A snowy deathrun map for all you runners out there. This is the second version of my first deathrun map, I hope I have brought you a fun and enjoyable map. I've tried to keep the icy theme throughout the map with the traps, endings and secrets, and would love to know what you think of it. Also, if you find any bugs, please report them to me on this website and I shall address them when I can. Please download and enjoy my map and let me know what you and your server communities think of it. Credits: Map design and creation by 'cS.Metz with special thanks to Fibbs and my friends for some trap ideas Map Details: - 15 traps (two skill/random) - 3 standard endings - 2 small secrets - 1 secret ending - AFK Timer (one minute) - Map Timer (five minutes) Update Log: v2fix - fixed Terrorist team bugs due to engine update v2 - Changed AWP/Knife endings - Added 3D Skybox - Disabled fall damage - Altered trap decals - Minor bug fixes - Damage per second traps now do more damage v1beta - Release version

So Of Course your asking... what the heck is in dr_hauntedmansion anyways?

Well

Traps include
Trap 1: Spirit Controller : You Take Controll of spirits that you navigate around with arrowkeys and try to hit players to teleport them to a haunted clock mountain which kills them!
Trap 2: Haunted Axe 1: Haunted Axe Flings down and players have to make sure they dont get hit!
Trap 3: Haunted Axe 2: Haunted Axe Flings down and players have to make sure they dont get hit!
Trap 4: Haunted Axe 3: Haunted Axe Flings down and players have to make sure they dont get hit!
Trap 5: Spooky Books 1: Books Fly out of there shelves and can kill players on touch
Trap 6: Spooky Books 2: Books Fly out of there shelves and can kill players on touch
Trap 7: Spooky Books 3: Books Fly out of there shelves and can kill players on touch
Trap 8: Disapearing Staircase: Scary Staircase moves players up.. but can dissapear and teleport players to a hauntlingly freaky death!
Trap 9: Zombie Shooter: Take Controll of the evil spirits once again to shoot zombie heads at cts
Trap 10: Lightning Strike: Hit Players With THE ALMIGHTY POWER OF LIGHTNING!!
Trap 11: Spinning Rocks Of Doom: Spinning rock knocks players off into aids infested water!
Trap 12: Piano Key 1: Piano Key shoots up To kill CTS
Trap 13: Piano Key 2: Piano Key shoots up To kill CTS
Trap 14: Piano Key 3: Piano Key shoots up To kill CTS
Trap 15: Piano Key 4: Piano Key shoots up To kill CTS
Trap 16: Electricity + Water: This is a more complex trap and very original.. there are 2 lines of electricity.. when the button is pressed eletric spark goes down and players have to jump when it touches the water or they get ZAPPED
Trap 17: Freaky Fireplace: When going through the fireplace press the button and the fireplace will close up behind them and they will be burned alive!!
Trap 18: Chandeler: Chandeler falls down breaking table
Trap 19: Haunted Sword 1: Haunted Swords Come Down on players from suits of armor...are they alive?
Trap 20: Haunted Sword 2: Haunted Swords Come Down on players from suits of armor...are they alive?
Trap 21: Haunted Sword 3: Haunted Swords Come Down on players from suits of armor...are they alive?
Trap 22: CRAZY BLACK GUY : Crazy black guy pops up from the abyse to kill and frighten players!
Trap 23: Zombie Head Appears And The Black part pushes you into him! very freaky!

Stages of map:
Stage 1: Cemetary
Stage 2: Haunted Mansion
Stage 3: Spooky Graveyard
Stage 4: The Part Of The house they dont want you to go..
Stage 5: Cave
Stage 6: Piano
Stage 7: The Soul Of The Demons
Stage 8: Are We back at the house?
Stage 9: Things Are getting messed up!
Stage 10: Abstract At It's Highest

Random Events:
Event 1: Evil Girl flys out at you
Event 2: Monster Clown Appears
Event 3: Ghost Train Passes By
Event 4: The room turns to blood!!
Event 5: Choose your fate as a 1/2 random trap decides whether you live..or DIE
Event 6: What was that?! A zombie flys by you
Event 7: Messed Up Creature Fly's Past Your face
Event 8: MASSIVE ZOMBIE APPEARS

Suprises:
i wont say but let's just say theres over 4 suprises in this map for you ;)

Secrets:
OVER 5 HIDDEN SECRETS

Ending MiniGames:
Climbing: skill jumping to get to the top where there is guns
Knife: Knife fight
AWP: use awps in a little map that looks really nice
